codex
I’ve got a concrete rewrite: keep the same Curve price-manipulation root cause and the vault/strategy probes, but replace the dead-end “existing balance only” path with a V2 flashswap arb that funds the manipulation and leaves real WETH on the verifier. I’m patching `FlawVerifier.sol` now and then I’ll sanity-check it for standalone compilation.
